[Yaxu increased by 12%]

277
00:21:20,330 --> 00:21:22,420
[Songtang decreased by 20% this year]

278
00:21:25,070 --> 00:21:30,160
Everyone, I do not agree to discontinuing Songtang.

279
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:32,280
Old Tang.

280
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:37,470
Isn't this data enough to clearly point out the problem?

281
00:21:37,470 --> 00:21:41,890
Old Xia, Songtang is the brand we started with when we built this enterprise.

282
00:21:41,890 --> 00:21:44,750
It's our start and foundation.

283
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:46,850
If we didn't have Songtang back then,

284
00:21:46,850 --> 00:21:51,050
we wouldn't have Mingyuan Fashion Group today.

285
00:21:51,050 --> 00:21:53,160
I just think that

286
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:55,230
if you continue to hold onto Songtang like this,

287
00:21:55,230 --> 00:21:58,870
in the end, what will be gone is our Mingyuan.

288
00:21:58,870 --> 00:22:03,500
Old Tang, I know that it's very important to globalize Chinoiserie.

289
00:22:03,500 --> 00:22:07,800
However, to shareholders like us, profit is more important.

290
00:22:13,370 --> 00:22:18,090
If I say I have a way for Songtang to overcome the current predicament

291
00:22:18,090 --> 00:22:22,920
and earn bigger profits, what would you all do?

292
00:22:23,950 --> 00:22:26,990
Mingxuan, continue.

293
00:22:31,820 --> 00:22:35,180
In the past few days, I've done a comprehensive analysis of Songtang.

294
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:39,880
If we break free from an inherent way of thinking when it comes to traditional Chinese clothing,

295
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:43,560
then starting from the clothing material to the traditional skills,

296
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:47,780
we can make overall changes to ultimately change Songtang's image.

297
00:22:47,780 --> 00:22:51,680
By elevating Songtang to a luxury level,

298
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:55,680
we'll have a win-win situation by bettering our reputation and profiting at the same time.

299
00:22:56,470 --> 00:22:59,690
How do you plan on realizing this dream of yours?

300
00:22:59,690 --> 00:23:02,570
There is a total of three steps. First:

301
00:23:02,570 --> 00:23:06,250
we have to have an in-depth collaboration with Fashion Daily.

302
00:23:06,250 --> 00:23:10,190
Songtang will be the first in a series of collaborations between Mingyuan

303
00:23:10,190 --> 00:23:12,360
and Fashion Daily.

304
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:18,670
Second: I insist on acquiring SLC. Third:

305
00:23:18,670 --> 00:23:23,330
our Mingyuan Fashion will promote a new variety show, called

306
00:23:23,330 --> 00:23:25,600
"Chinese Fashion."

307
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:29,530
Through this program, we will be able to use television and internet platforms

308
00:23:29,530 --> 00:23:31,500
to publicize and market.

309
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:33,700
At the same time, we will choose

310
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:38,230
some young, talented, and passionate participants to enter Songtang.

311
00:23:38,230 --> 00:23:43,240
Our Songtang will have a makeover.

312
00:23:48,770 --> 00:23:52,800
Mingxuan, are you confident?

313
00:23:53,660 --> 00:23:56,130
Dad, is there anything you are worried about?

314
00:23:57,690 --> 00:24:00,070
I am old now.

315
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:04,700
If it were 10 years ago, I would surely support you.

316
00:24:04,700 --> 00:24:08,560
Also, I would take the chance with you.

317
00:24:09,470 --> 00:24:13,040
Right now, you need to know that every decision you make

318
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:17,000
is connected to your future and fate here at Mingyuan.

319
00:24:18,820 --> 00:24:22,370
I think what you discussed with me last time makes a lot of sense.

320
00:24:22,370 --> 00:24:26,850
You, me, Songtang, as well as Mingyuan.

321
00:24:26,850 --> 00:24:29,470
We're destined to be inseparable.

322
00:24:29,470 --> 00:24:31,880
If Mingyuan doesn't have Songtang today,

323
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:34,190
then would it still be Mingyuan?

324
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:37,470
So I am willing to take a gamble.

325
00:24:38,190 --> 00:24:42,140
Earlier at the meeting, you mentioned SLC.

326
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:45,630
