338
00:25:25,710 --> 00:25:28,860
You're talking about veteran craftsmen?

339
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:30,850
Because of some historical reasons,

340
00:25:30,850 --> 00:25:34,170
most of them are operated by families.

341
00:25:34,170 --> 00:25:38,110
