343
00:25:39,870 --> 00:25:43,000
I just need to do whatever I can to meet their requirements.

344
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,220
This is not what I mean.

345
00:25:45,220 --> 00:25:47,800
I am talking about humanity.

346
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:52,040
Business is business, why talk about humanity?

347
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:55,840
Look, you are still young.

348
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:58,340
In the past, I was like you.

349
00:25:58,340 --> 00:26:00,910
What I am worried most about right now is

350
00:26:00,910 --> 00:26:04,000
your nature to divide things so clearly.

351
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:08,920
You have to know if you speak like this to those veteran craftsmen, you won't get anywhere with them.

352
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:15,200
Compared to business, what they may view as more important are feelings and sentiments.

353
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:18,870
Remember, feelings and sentiments.

354
00:26:18,870 --> 00:26:22,750
Enough. Stop lecturing me, Old Dad.

355
00:26:23,370 --> 00:26:25,580
Here, have a sip.

356
00:26:32,430 --> 00:26:34,390
Are you used to it?

357
