376
00:27:53,210 --> 00:27:56,660
You... You're Fang Xiaoyu?

377
00:27:56,660 --> 00:27:59,390
You're the gifted designer who got the France Youth Design Award at

378
00:27:59,390 --> 00:28:02,010
