379
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:08,560
This gown is not bad. Two days ago, Teacher Pan and I were even praising it.

380
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:12,490
Clothing still has to be worn by people.

381
00:28:12,490 --> 00:28:16,650
Some designers have too many opinions.

382
00:28:16,650 --> 00:28:20,360
