387
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:40,970
But it still didn't affect your potential, isn't that right?

388
00:28:40,970 --> 00:28:43,250
Thank you, Director Fang.

389
00:28:43,250 --> 00:28:46,350
Do you have time for coffee?

390
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:49,750
But I am not finished here.

391
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:53,950
