- I'm leaving now.

416
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:20,460
- Take care, bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

417
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:36,130
Mo Fei!

418
00:30:36,130 --> 00:30:38,000
